history.content:
(U)GSI, Group Tutor, and Reader applications for Data C8, C100/200, C140 (formerly Stat 140 a.k.a. Prob 140) and C102 are live.

There are two forms to fill out: the main form linked above, and the CDSS Supplemental info form linked at the bottom of the main form.

Note the short turnaround: the priority deadline is October 30.

Data course staff are outstanding and being on staff is a great experience. I hope you will apply. If you have questions, please register for our AMA this afternoon: @3160

Thank you!
